'''Denethor''' can refer to three characters:
* [[Denethor (Nando)|Denethor]], son of [[Lenwë]] and leader of the [[Laiquendi]] who was killed in the [[First Battle of Beleriand]].
* [[Denethor I]] ({{TA|2375}} - {{TA|2477|n}}), tenth [[Ruling Steward]] of [[Gondor]].
* '''[[Denethor|Denethor II]] ({{TA|2930}}- {{TA|3019|n}}), twenty-sixth Ruling Steward of Gondor during the [[War of the Ring]], and father of [[Boromir]] and [[Faramir]].'''
